---
const lineLink = 'https://line.me/R/ti/p/@782faclv';
const igLink = 'https://www.instagram.com/meet_misaki0112';

const footerLinks = {
  services: [
    { href: '/services/eyelash', label: '超持久美睫' },
    { href: '/services/embroidery', label: '半永久紋綉' },
    { href: '/services/beauty', label: '美容美體' },
  ],
  quick: [
    { href: '/about', label: '關於我們' },
    { href: '/portfolio', label: '作品集' },
    { href: '/faq', label: '常見問題' },
  ],
};
---

<footer class="bg-mi-dark text-white/70">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pt-16 pb-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-12">
      <!-- Brand -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-1">
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2.5 font-bold text-xl text-white mb-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gold-gradient flex items-center justify-center text-white text-lg">Mi</div>
          <span>遇見Mi美學館</span>
        </a>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
          全台北公認最持久睫毛，一站式美學服務。<br>
          讓妳不用跑很多地方，也能享受全方位的美麗。
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <a href={igLink} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-mi-pink transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1" aria-label="Instagram">
            IG
          </a>
          <a href={lineLink} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-[#06C755] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1" aria-label="LINE">
            <span class="text-sm font-bold">L</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Services -->
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-white font-semibold text-lg mb-5">服務項目</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          {footerLinks.services.map(link => (
            <li><a href={link.href} class="text-sm hover:text-mi-pink transition-colors duration-300">{link.label}</a></li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Quick Links -->
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-white font-semibold text-lg mb-5">快速連結</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          {footerLinks.quick.map(link => (
            <li><a href={link.href} class="text-sm hover:text-mi-pink transition-colors duration-300">{link.label}</a></li>
          ))}
          <li><a href={lineLink} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sm hover:text-mi-pink transition-colors duration-300">LINE預約</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Contact -->
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-white font-semibold text-lg mb-5">聯絡我們</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-mi-pink flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">📍</span>
            <span>台北市大同區民生西路94號2樓<br>（雙連站1號出口30秒）</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-mi-pink flex-shrink-0">📞</span>
            <span>0989-260-867</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-mi-pink flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">⏰</span>
            <span>週一至週日 11:00-20:00<br>（完全預約制）</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="border-t border-white/10 pt-8 text-center text-sm">
      <p>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} 遇見Mi美學館 版權所有 | 統一編號認證</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
